dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Tiled Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for Jackson County, WI 2022
dc_description_s: This data represents a LiDAR-derived tiled Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for Jackson County, Wisconsin in 2022. A DEM represents the bare-Earth surface, removing all natural and built features.
uw_supplemental_s: For original vendor XML metadata please visit: https://web.s3.wisc.edu/wsco-wisconsinview/lidar/Jackson/Jackson_2022_3DEP_Delivery/Metadata/Metadata.zip
